## Repo Setup

Move `{{ repo.agentFile }}.md` to your repo root. Leave everything else in `/midtempo-framework/`.

Then run setup:
```
Setup Stage 1 using `/midtempo-framework/setup.md`
```

[Full install instructions](INSTALL.md).

> I purposely haven't integrated this with VSCode, Claude Code, or any other solution. There are no slash-commands, dependencies to install, or code to run. The framework is purely markdown (text) documents that act together as complex prompts. There should be no security risks or red flags with this framework. Either call the skills by path or file name (as provided), or integrate with your environment as you see fit.

