## Updating Framework

**Website**: 

- upload the `midtempo-framework.yml`
- edit/ensure it's up-to-date 
- generate 
- unpack the zip into your repo
- move `{{ repo.agentFile }}.md` to your repo root. 
- make sure that the `midtempo-framework/instructions/` folder is untouched

**CLI**: 
- put latest `midtempo-framework.yml`into `agents/{repo.name}` folder
- run `npm run generate {repo.name}`
- copy contents of `agents/{repo.name}` to repo
- move `{{ repo.agentFile }}.md` to your repo root. 
- make sure that the `midtempo-framework/instructions/` folder is untouched

