## Key Files

```
/
├── {{ repo.agentFile }}.md         # Agent rules (must be in repo root)
├── midtempo-framework/
│   ├── midtempo-framework.yml      # Your repo's configuration
│   ├── instructions/               # Immutable repo grounding docs (created by `setup.md`)
│   ├── rules/                      # Coding standards the agent enforces
│   └── templates/                  # Document templates for each pipeline step
└── planning/                       # Only *-design.md committed; rest gitignored
    ├── [feature]-decisions.md      # What to build and why
    ├── [feature]-design.md         # Technical design (source of truth)
    ├── [feature]-plan.md           # Step-by-step delivery plan
    ├── [feature]-tests.md          # Test scenarios (Given/When/Then)
    ├── investigations/             # Investigation reports and recommendations
    ├── reviews/                    # Review reports and recommendations
    └── archive/                    # Old design docs (subfolders ftw!)
```

