## Sizing Your Work

Keep features to **30 unit tests or fewer** per build. Use `investigate.md` to break larger work into smaller pieces.

Oversized features blow through context windows and need constant intervention. Breaking things into sensible chunks means better results and less time fixing the agent's drift.

